                        <interp inst="t18500819-name-669" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN LEWIS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City policeman,</hi> 431). I produce a certificate (<hi rend="italic">read—Moses Nathan, convicted here July, 1847, and Confined Six Months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
